title: Did El Chapo offer millions to the Clinton Foundation?
subtitle: Julian Assange launched an attack on the safety of the Clinton Foundation with the latest intelligence report that says the organization has ties to the leader of the Mexican drug cartel Joaquin Chapo Guzman.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: Mexican drug king Joaquin "El Chapo" Guzmán donated millions of dollars to the Clinton Foundation.
